    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "### Example 3: \"The Mystery of the Missing Cupcake\" \r\n\r\n**Narrative:** The player is a detective solving the case of a stolen cupcake. They interrogate suspects, gather clues, and make decisions that lead to different suspects being accused.\r\n\r\n**Key Features:**\r\n- Three interrogation questions with two possible answers each\r\n- Uses conditionals to track clues and determine the outcome\r\n- Fun and light-hearted, with simple logic puzzles",
    "ai_tutor_available": "false",
